  Title: God in All Worlds
  Locus:
    Page: 54
  Source:
    Title: THje Seven Storey Mountain
By: Thomas Merton
---
A soul is an immaterial thing. It is a principle of activity, it is an
“act,” a “form,” an energizing principle. It is the life of the body,
and it must also have a life ofits own. But the life of the soul does not
inhere in any physical, material subject.
